3 x 7 card tableau
------------------------
Foundation 7s: (0, 1), (0, 3), (2, 1), (2, 3)
Foundation 6:  (1, 2)
Tableau:       (0, 2), (1, 1), (1, 3), (2, 2)
Stock:         (0, 5)
Waste pile:    (0, 6)
Parking:       (2, 6)

With the same margin in x- and y-led.
Offset in y-led.
Foundation7s outwards offset.

cardHeight = 96
cardWidth = 71

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Foundation 7s
(0, 1), (0, 3), (2, 1), (2, 3)
(cardWidth + 2 * margin - offset, margin)
(3 * cardWidth + 4 * margin + offset, margin)
(cardWidth + 2 * margin - offset, 2 * cardHeight + 3 * margin + 2 * offset)
(3 * cardWidth + 4 * margin + offset, 2 * cardHeight + 3 * margin + 2 * offset)
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Foundation 6
(1, 2)
(2 * cardWidth + 3 * margin, cardHeight+ 2 * margin + offset)
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Tableau
(0, 2), (1, 1), (1, 3), (2, 2)
(2 * cardWidth + 3 * margin, margin + offset)
(cardWidth + 2 * margin, cardHeight+ 2 * margin + offset)
(3 * cardWidth + 4 * margin, cardHeight+ 2 * margin + offset)
(2 * cardWidth + 3 * margin, 2 * cardHeight + 3 * margin + offset)
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Stock
(0, 5)
(5 * cardWidth + 6 * margin, margin + offset)
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Waste pile
(0, 6)
(6 * cardWidth + 7 * margin, margin + offset)
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Parking
(2, 6)
(6 * cardWidth + 7 * margin, 2 * cardHeight + 3 * margin + offset)
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

